    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People who watch other people or situations secretly or in stealth, usually such people having this as a career or who are otherwise rewarded for the work. Examples are secret agents employed by a government in order to obtain information relating to military affairs or to collect other intelligence. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
